"Hatsukari": "I figured the fighting would die down a bit ever since the mission into Stia's interior, but..."
"It feels like somehow it's actually gotten busier, don't it?"
"Either way, let's work together and get through this."
"Even though that strong enemy got smacked down, the fighting's hardly died down at all!"
"But hey, my crew's always rarin' to go, so it works out."
"Our mission right now's an enemy sweep-up operation in Dext Base."
"That place is still chock-full of enemies."
"What do you say? You want in on this?"
"The targets are the enemies in Dext Base. You got this?"
"Measure your strength with the strength of your enemies. Don't overextend, and you're golden."
"Oh, you're busy? Makes sense. I doubt I'm the only one who's been relyin' on your help."
"The fightin' in Stia still hasn't died down."
"But, thanks to you, it's better than it used to be."
"In other words, things've probably just broke even. Hahaha!"
